_ci/
compiler/out/

# NOTE: small example compiler outputs under examples/out_* ARE committed on purpose as
# browsable reference artifacts (protocol.md, diagnostics.md, staples.csv, sequences...).
# But the bulky, regenerable 3D-coordinate files are ignored so they don't spam every
# future diff with ~240 KB of numbers each time examples are regenerated:
examples/out_*/conf.dat
examples/out_*/structure.pdb
# Delete the line below to ignore example outputs entirely.
# examples/out_*/
